caption.text: If someone ask me when i met Her for the first time? Well, saya inget banget waktu pertama kali ketemu dia pas di asrama. Waktu itu hari 1 kami masuk asrama dan saya melihat dia sedang sibuk membereskan tempat tidurnya. I choose to sleep under Her At That time. Then, As time passed By i realized That she is one of My clasmate, so i asked Her to be My chairmate.  Adaptasi sama Melda ngga susah karena memang dia orang yang open minded dan ceria. She is like to joke around me and Also Cheer me up whenever I'm Down üòÇ. Walaupun kelas XI & XII kami terpisah, but we are still keep in touch everyday because we Used to go to school together and have a Quality time every weekend. Melda adalah salah satu orang yang sangat mensupport program saya untuk "change My life style to be healthy". She is the one Who always try to hold me and keep me on the right track until i got My target. Beside That kami juga punya banyak kesamaan salah satunya bercita" untuk masuk ke suatu univ yang sama. Tapi ternyata Allah punya rencana lebih indah, kami pada akhirnya terpisahkan oleh Waktu Dan jarak (me still in Sumatera but Melda had to move to Java). Even though we are a thousand miles apart but we are still same, we are still close, we are still care to each other, and we are always try to have a quality time when holiday is coming. I'm so grateful to have such a good friend like her in my life and I'm looking forward your graduation next year, mel! Haha
